nsider.com%2F679bf834196626c40985e647%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223071%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E12th%20Army%20Aviation%20Battalion%20UH-60%20Blackhawk%20helicopters%20fly%20in%20formation%20over%20the%20Potomac%20River%20in%20Washington.%3Cp%3EU.S.%20Army%20photo%20by%20Bernardo%20Fuller%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20Army%20Black%20Hawk%20that%20collided%20with%20an%20American%20Airlines%20flight%20was%20training%20on%20a%20familiar%20flight%20path.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%2012th%20Aviation%20Battalion%20frequently%20navigates%20Washington%20DC%20airspace%20for%20VIP%20transport.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPilots%20were%20flying%20with%20night%20vision%20goggles%20and%20are%20trained%20to%20deal%20with%20those%20challenges.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Army%20crew%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-a-black-hawk-helicopter-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUH-60%20Black%20Hawk%3C%2Fa%3E%20helicopter%20that%20fatally%20collided%20with%20an%20American%20Airlines%20passenger%20jet%20on%20Wednesday%20was%20on%20a%20routine%20training%20flight%20on%20a%20well-known%20flight%20path%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20an%20Army%20official%20said%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJonathan%20Koziol%2C%20a%20retired%20Army%20chief%20warrant%20officer%20aviator%20with%20nearly%20three%20decades%20of%20military%20flight%20experience%2C%20said%20during%20a%20media%20roundtable%20this%20flight%20would%20have%20likely%20been%20deemed%20%26quot%3Blow%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20not%20medium%20or%20high%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20designations%20are%20required%20elements%20of%20pre-flight%20risk%20assessments%20and%20briefings%20to%20military%20mission%20approval%20authorities%20and%20take%20into%20account%20variables%20like%20weather%2C%20mission%20type%2C%20and%20potential%20hazards.%20Koziol%2C%20the%20Headquarters%20Department%20of%20the%20Army%20Aviation%20Directorate%20Chief%20of%20Staff%2C%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20flight%20operation%20or%20oversight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecretary%20of%20Defense%20Pete%20Hegseth%20said%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%20that%20the%20flight%20was%20%26quot%3Broutine%26quot%3B%20and%20conducted%20along%20a%20%26quot%3Bstandard%26quot%3B%20corridor.%20The%20flight%20was%20along%20Route%204%2C%20a%20commonly%20used%20flight%20path%2C%20and%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3Eshould%20not%20have%20been%20a%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20Koziol%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrews%20from%20the%20Army's%2012th%20Aviation%20Battalion%2C%20based%20in%20Ft.%20Belvoir%2C%20Virginia%2C%20are%20well%20acquainted%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdc-plane-crash-military-training-congested-airspace-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWashington%2C%20DC%20and%20the%20surrounding%20areas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20Koziol.%20Much%20of%20this%20unit's%20mission%20includes%20ferrying%20government%20and%20military%20VIPs%20throughout%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR)%20and%20being%20ready%20to%20move%20officials%20during%20crises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20the%20Black%20Hawk's%20flight%20path%2C%20Koziol%20said%20%26quot%3Bthis%20is%20a%20relatively%20easy%20corridor%20to%20fly%20because%20you're%20flying%20down%20the%20center%20of%20the%20river.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22612%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Emergency%20responders%20in%20boats%20near%20a%20damaged%20aircraft%20in%20the%20water%20at%20night%20with%20an%20airport%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679b13cc196626c40985c224%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22408%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEmergency%20response%20units%20assess%20aircraft%20wreckage%20in%20the%20Potomac%20River%20after%20an%20American%20Airlines%20flight%20from%20Wichita%2C%20Kansas%20collided%20with%20a%20helicopter%20while%20approaching%20Ronald%20Reagan%20National%20Airport.%3Cp%3E(Photo%20by%20Andrew%20Harnik%2FGetty%20Images)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20dark%20river%20flight%20path%2C%20with%20urban%20lights%20on%20either%20side%20to%20act%20as%20informal%20guardrails%2C%20makes%20the%20task%20simple%20for%20pilots.%20The%20battalion's%20Black%20Hawk%20was%20also%20equipped%20with%20an%20in-flight%20map%2C%20meaning%20the%20pilots%20could%20track%20their%20position%20throughout%20the%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20the%20darkness%20of%20the%20river%2C%20and%20you%20have%20the%20lights%20on%20either%20side%20of%20you%20and%20obviously%20the%20rotating%20beacon%20on%20Reagan%20National%20to%20point%20out%20the%20airfield%20and%20all%20the%20traffic%20on%20it%20for%20them%20to%20know%20exactly%20where%20they're%20at%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20routes%20for%20helicopters%20in%20the%20NCR%20which%20government%20aircraft%20traverse%20daily%20and%20includes%20airspace%20that%20is%20off-limits%20to%20non-approved%20aircraft%2C%20including%20areas%20near%20the%20Pentagon%2C%20White%20House%2C%20National%20Mall%2C%20and%20Naval%20Observatory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20flight%20requires%20coordination%20with%20surrounding%20air%20traffic%20control%2C%20including%20the%20Ronald%20Reagan%20Washington%20National%20Airport%2C%20which%20assigns%20each%20flight%20a%20four-digit%20tracking%20number%20to%20chart%20its%20movements.%20Within%20the%20aviation%20unit%2C%20flights%20are%20meticulously%20planned%20for%20and%20managed%2C%20Koziol%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKoziol%20said%20the%20Black%20Hawk%20pilots%20were%20training%20with%20night%20vision%20goggles%2C%20which%20can%20cut%20down%20a%20wearer's%20peripheral%20vision%20and%20impact%20depth%20perception.%20Soldiers%20train%20regularly%20with%20these%20capabilities%20to%20limit%20the%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20helpful%20at%20night%2C%20obviously%2C%20and%20in%20an%20urban%20environment%2C%20they're%20still%20useful%2C%26quot%3B%20Koziol%20said.%20City%20lights%20can%20make%20seeing%20with%20night%20vision%20more%20difficult%2C%20but%20flying%20over%20the%20river%20where%20the%20Black%20Hawk%20was%20shouldn't%20have%20posed%20any%20problems%20with%20light%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20crew%20members%2C%20two%20pilots%20and%20a%20crew%20chief%2C%20were%20experienced%20aviators%2C%20he%20said.%20Both%20pilots%20had%20at%20least%201500%20combined%20flight%20hours%20between%20them.%20One%20pilot%20served%20as%20the%20flight%20commander%20and%20instructor%2C%20overseeing%20an%20annual%20training%20requirement%20for%20the%20second%20pilot%2C%20who%20held%20500%20hours%20and%20had%20previously%20served%20as%20a%20flight%20commander.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cause%20of%20Wednesday's%20deadly%20crash%2C%20in%20which%20there%20were%20no%20survivors%2C%20is%20unknown%20and%20under%20investigation.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrashed-black-hawks-flight-path-wasnt-complicated-army-official-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738276019000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679bfb3aeb4be2fff9a3065b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrashed-black-hawks-flight-path-wasnt-complicated-army-official-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Army%20official%20said%20that%20the%20pilots%20were%20on%20a%20routine%20training%20flight%20along%20a%20familiar%20flight%20path%20that%20isn't%20particularly%20complicated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kbaker%40insider.com%20(Kelsey%20Baker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrashed-black-hawks-flight-path-wasnt-complicated-army-official-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Best%20Picture%20Battle%3A%20Six%20Movies%20Have%20a