%20than%20%242.6%20million%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fs3.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F25509708%2Fkash-patel-financial-disclosure.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20disclosure%3C%2Fa%3E%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider%20ahead%20of%20its%20public%20release%2C%20Patel's%20income%20came%20from%20a%20mixture%20of%20consulting%20work%2C%20paid%20speeches%2C%20media%20appearances%2C%20and%20the%20proceeds%20of%20several%20books.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20total%20net%20worth%20is%20more%20than%20%245.9%20million%2C%20according%20to%20a%20document%20filed%20with%20the%20Senate%20Judiciary%20Committee.%20All%20of%20Trump's%20nominees%20are%20required%20to%20file%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-administration-nominee-financial-disclosures-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublic%20final%20disclosure%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20they%20are%20considered%20by%20the%20Senate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bulk%20of%20Patel's%20income%2C%20more%20than%20%242.1%20million%2C%20came%20from%20consulting%20work.%20Among%20his%20clients%20was%20Trump%20Media%20and%20Technology%20Corp%2C%20the%20company%20that%20runs%20Truth%20Social.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F1849635%2F000114036124030406%2Fny20026576x34_s1a.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiling%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%2C%20Patel's%20annual%20compensation%20was%20%24120%2C000%2C%20though%20his%20contract%20ended%20in%20March%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpam-bondi-truth-social-stock-lobbying-financial-disclosure-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPam%20Bondi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Trump's%20nominee%20for%20attorney%20general%2C%20has%20also%20been%20financially%20tied%20up%20with%20Truth%20Social%2C%20holding%20more%20than%20%243.9%20million%20i