20began%20to%20piece%20together%20how%20a%20military%20helicopter%20collided%20with%20the%20regional%20jet%2C%20questions%20swirled%20about%20communication%20between%20the%20pilots%20and%20Reagan%20National%20Airport's%20control%20tower.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESen.%20Tammy%20Duckworth%2C%20an%20ex-Army%20Black%20Hawk%20helicopter%20pilot%2C%20told%20reporters%20that%20military%20aircraft%20usually%20do%20not%20talk%20directly%20to%20commercial%20pilots%2C%20as%20ATC%20is%20the%20responsible%20intermediary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody's%20listening%20on%20the%20same%20frequency%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20American%20flight%20that%20crashed%20would%20have%20been%20aware%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-a-black-hawk-helicopter-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBlack%20Hawk%20helicopter%20in%20the%20skies%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20listening%20to%20instructions%20from%20ATC.%20ATC%20is%20telling%20you%20what%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuckworth%20said%20an%20FAA%20briefing%20involving%20ATC%20tapes%20revealed%20the%20helicopter%20pilots%20were%20told%20about%20the%20passenger%20plane%2C%20and%20the%20crew%20confirmed%20%26quot%3Bat%20least%20twice%26quot%3B%20that%20they%20had%20the%20jet%20in%20sight%20before%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20the%20American%20flight%20was%20cleared%20to%20land%20and%20would%20have%20had%20the%20%26quot%3Bright%20of%20way%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20Black%20Hawk%20was%20told%20to%20pass%20behind.%20The%20flight%20was%20in%20visual%20flight%20conditions%2C%20meaning%20the%20helicopter%20would%20be%20visually%20searching%20for%20the%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20would%20be%20looking%20up%20to%20try%20to%20find%20this%20aircraft%2C%20pick%20it%20out%20of%20the%20sky%20as%20it's%20coming%20in%20for%20a%20landing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Admini