-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Euncertain%20future%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20President%20Trump%20signed%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-trump-app-store-return-apple-google-legal-risk-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eexecutive%20order%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20January%2020%20that%20gave%20TikTok%2075%20more%20days%20to%20operate%20in%20the%20US%2C%20as%20owner%20ByteDance%20will%20either%20have%20to%20divest%20from%20TikTok%20or%20it%20will%20be%20banned%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20have%20control%20of%20what's%20going%20to%20happen%20to%20Tiktok%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20competitors%2C%20but%20they're%20an%20important%20one.%20So%2C%20who's%20gonna%20own%20Tiktok%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%3F%20What's%20gonna%20happen%3F%20I%20mean%2C%20that's%20a%20pretty%20big%20deal%2C%20something%20that's%20a%20card%20that%20we%20get%20to%20turn%20over.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20Zuckerberg%20emphasized%20that%20the%20company%20needs%20to%20avoid%20taking%20%26quot%3Btoo%20narrow%20of%20a%20view%26quot%3B%20of%20social%20interaction%20as%20it%20navigates%20the%20emergence%20of%20AI.%20He%20outlined%20a%20vision%20for%20AI-powered%20features%20in%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%20feeds%2C%20including%20interactive%20AI%20agents%20that%20users%20can%20converse%20with%20and%20more%20immersive%20content%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20next%20trend%20here%20is%20there're%20going%20to%20be%20things%20that%20either%20AI%20can%20produce%2C%20that%20we%20can%20just%20put%20in%20there...%20I%20think%20this%20year%20we're%20gonna%20have%20stuff%20where%20it's%20like%2C%20okay%2C%20you%20have%20an%20AI%20agent%2C%20and%20you%20can%20just%20start%20talking%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3