l%20citrate%20%26quot%3Bhelps%20prevent%20the%20breakdown%20of%20sweat%20into%20odor-causing%20compounds%2C%20so%20it%20decreases%20odor%20from%20underarm%20sweat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2239bf2f36-7831-4056-9c28-41907a9b452a%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20a%20ton%20of%20fragrance%20options%20for%20every%20kind%20of%20preference.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20the%20Orange%20Neroli%20and%20Grapefruit%20Cassis%20scents%2C%20but%20the%20White%20Tea%20is%20also%20a%20fan%20favorite.%20There%20are%20several%20other%20options%2C%20like%20coconut%2C%20vanilla%2C%20eucalyptus%2C%20and%20peach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20fellow%20editor%2C%20Maiya%20Pascouche%2C%20tested%20out%20the%20Peach%20Soleil%20scent%20and%20wasn't%20a%20big%20fan%2C%20so%20the%20fragrances%20can%20be%20hit%20or%20miss%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20if%20they%20just%20don't%20mix%20well%20with%20your%20body%20chemistry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222beef1fe-d567-4a7a-90f5-015c7e807c8d%5C%22%3ECurie%20has%20several%20other%20products%2C%20including%20a%20stick%20version%20of%20their%20deodorant%2C%20but%20I%20definitely%20prefer%20the%20spray.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20holds%20two%20bottles%20of%20Curie%20Stick%20Deodorant%20and%20Dry%20Shampoo%20in%20their%20hand%20against%20a%20green-patterned%20bathroom%20wall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679bd738eb4be2fff9a2f941%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECurie%20started%20with%20a%20stick%20formula%20first%2C%20but%20I%20have%20to%20say%2C%20it's%20not%20my%20favorite.%20The%20inclusion%20of%20baking%20soda%20in%20the%20stick%20version%20is%20slightly%20irritating%20to%20my%20skin%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20find%20that%20it%20helped%20with%20odor%20control%20(even%20after%20testing%20multiple%20fragrances).%20The%20arrowro