flight%20at%20Axiom%20Space%2C%20will%20command%20the%20private%20Ax-4%20mission%2C%20while%20Group%20Captain%20Shukla%20will%20serve%20as%20pilot%2C%20the%20American%20space%20agency%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20really%20excited%20to%20go%20into%20microgravity%20and%20experience%20space%20flight%20on%20my%20own.%20The%20tempo%20for%20the%20mission%20has%20been%20building%20up%20each%20month.%20I%20think%20we%20are%20at%20a%20stage%20wherein%20all%20the%20pieces%20are%20kind%20of%20coming%20together.%20I'm%20extremely%20excited%20to%20see%20how%20this%20unfolds%20in%20the%20coming%20months%20and%20for%20the%20actual%20space%20flight%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Group%20Captain%20Shukla%20said%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question%20by%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fvmfklp7o_axiom-4_625x300_30_January_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Axiom%204%20Mission%20team%20speaks%20to%20NDTV%20Science%20Editor%20Pallava%20Bagla%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20training%20for%20the%20past%20four-five%20months.%20We%20now%20understand%20the%20entire%20CONOPS%2C%20the%20concept%20of%20operations%2C%20and%20going%20forward%20from%20here%20it%20would%20mostly%20be%20repetition%20of%20the%20things%20that%20we%20have%20done.%20So%20we%20are%20ready%20and%20confident%20in%20our%20abilities%20to%20execute%20this%20mission%20successfully%2C%26quot%3B%20Group%20Captain%20Shukla%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20whether%20he%20would%20perform%20yoga%20as%20was%20done%20by%20Wing%20Commander%20Rakesh%20Sharma%20in%20space%2C%20Group%20Captain%20Shukla%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20now%20that%20you%20have%20said%20so%2C%20I%20would%20probably%20demonstrate%20a%20few%20poses%20of%20yoga%2