ice%20action%20has%20cost%20him%20his%20job%20and%20a%20marriage%20proposal%2C%20brought%20immense%20disrepute%20to%20his%20family%2C%20and%20left%20him%20with%20an%20%26quot%3Bunbearable%20dangerous%20feeling%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Akash%20Kanojia%2C%20who%20was%20briefly%20detained%20and%20interrogated%2C%20said%20his%20photograph%20was%20widely%20circulated%20despite%20having%20no%20involvement%20in%20the%20crime.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20was%20my%20photo%20made%20viral%3F%20I%20want%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20threatening%20to%20move%20court%20if%20his%20photograph%20was%20not%20brought%20down%20by%20all%20those%20who%20shared%20it%20across%20various%20online%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20sought%20to%20know%20if%20police%20would%20have%20acted%20in%20a%20similar%20way%20had%20a%20VIP%20or%20a%20millionaire's%20son%20been%20a%20suspect%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2018%2C%20Mr%20Kanojia%20was%20detained%20from%20Mumbai%20Lokmanya%20Tilak%20Terminus-Kolkata%20Shalimar%20Jnaneswari%20Express%20at%20Chhattisgarh's%20Durg%20station%20by%20the%20Railway%20Protection%20Force%20(RPF)%20after%20a%20tip%20off%20from%20Mumbai%20police%2C%20two%20days%20after%20Mr%20Khan%20was%20stabbed%20by%20an%20intruder%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20Bandra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20released%20a%20day%20later%2C%20with%20Mumbai%20Police%20officials%20saying%20he%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwas-just-a-suspect-man-detained-from-chhattisgarh-in-saif-ali-khan-attack-case-released-7508817%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejust%20a%20suspect%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Days%20later%20and%20after%20over%2070%20hours%20of%20an%20intense%20manhunt%2C%20a%2030-year-old%20man%2C%20who%20was%20later%20identified%20as%20a%20Bangladeshi%20national%2C%20was%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kanojia%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20police%20action%20had%20severe%20repercussions%20and%20left%20him%20and%20his%20family%20traumatised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20lost%20his%20job%20as%20a%20driver.%20He%20said%20his%20marriage%20was%20fixed%20but%20the%20prospective%20bride's%20family%20called%20it%20off%20after%20he%20was%20detained%20in%20the%20case.%20He%20added%20that%20his%20relatives%20and%20friends%20are%20hesitant%20to%20meet%20or%20maintain%20ties%20with%20him%20and%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhatever%20happened%20to%20me%20should%20not%20happen%20to%20anyone%20else.%20I%20am%20a%20poor%20man%2C%20and%20that's%20why%20I%20had%20to%20see%20such%20days.%20What%20if%20there%20was%20a%20VIP%20or%20a%20millionaire's%20son%20in%20my%20place%2C%20what%20would%20they%20(police)%20have%20done%3F%20Such%20things%20happened%20to%20me%20today%20but%20they%20should%20not%20happen%20to%20anyone%20tomorrow.%20After%20such%20treatment%2C%20that%20dangerous%20feeling%20you%20get%20is%20unbearable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20defamed%20so%20much.%20It%20is%20a%20question%20of%20someone's%20life.%20I%20was%20not%20wrong.%20I%20had%20not%20committed%20any%20crime.%20Then%20why%20was%20my%20photo%20made%20viral%3F%20I%20am%20not%20capable%20of%20committing%20such%20crimes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20requested%20all%20those%20who%20circulated%20his%20photograph%20across%20platforms%20to%20delete%20it.%20%26quot%3BOtherwise%20there%20is%20only%20one%20last%20stop%20-%20court.%20I'll%20have%20to%20knock%20on%20the%20court's%20door%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kanojia%20recalled%20the%20events%20that%20led%20to%20his%20detention.%20He%20said%20he%20was%20travelling%20on%20the%20Mumbai%20Lokmanya%20Tilak%20Terminus-Kolkata%20Shalimar%20Jnaneshwari%20Express%20when%20he%20was%20cornered%20by%20the%20RPF%20men.%20%26quot%3BThey%20showed%20me%20my%20photograph.%20I%20told%20him%20I%20am%20Akash%20Kanojia.%20They%20asked%20me%20to%20get%20off%20the%20train.%20When%20I%20asked%20them%20why%2C%20they%20said%20the%20Mumbai%20Police%20have%20asked%20them%20to%20locate%20me.%20Since%20I%20knew%20that%20the%20RPF%20was%20doing%20its%20duty%2C%20I%20agreed%20to%20go%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20this%2C%20the%20RPF%20took%20me%20with%20them.%20They%20told%20me%20that%20they%20would%20not%20ask%20me%20anything%20or%20initiate%20any%20action%20against%20me.%20They%20asked%20if%20I%20was%20just%20running%20away%3F%20I%20asked%20them%20why%20would%20I%20run%3F%20I%20told%20them%20that%20if%20they%20think%20I%20have%20done%20something%20wrong%2C%20then%20they%20should%20call%20the%20Mumbai%20cops.%20As%20the%20cops%20came%2C%20I%20was%20interrogated.%20I%20told%20them%20I%20did%20not%20commit%20the%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kanojia%20said%20he%20asked%20the%20cops%20to%20take%20him%20to%20the%20actor%20to%20verify%20if%20he%20had%20carried%20out%20the%20attack.%20%26quot%3BI%20said%20that%20if%20he%20(Mr%20Khan)%20says%20that%20it%20was%20me%20who%20attacked%20him%2C%20then%20the%20police%20can%20blame%20me%20for%20all%20the%20crimes%20that%20took%20place%20in%20Mumbai%20that%20day.%20Why%20should%20I%20accept%20something%20that%20I%20have%20not%20done.%20After%20this%2C%20I%20was%20allowed%20to%20go%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kanojia's%20father%2C%20Kailash%2C%20earlier%20criticised%20the%20cops%20for%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsaif-ali-khan-attack-case-ruined-my-sons-life-father-of-man-detained-released-in-saif-attack-case-7573719%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eruining%20my%20son's%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20police%20detained%20my%20son%20without%20verifying%20his%20identity.%20This%20mistake%20has%20ruined%20his%20life.%20Now%2C