0respond%20to%20all%20appropriate%20requests%20from%20lawmakers%2C%20aiming%20to%20safeguard%20communities%20and%20improve%20credibility.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fkash-patel-confirmation-hearing-donald-trumps-fbi-chief-pick-pledges-reform-vows-transparency%2Farticleshow%2F117748384.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fkash-patel-confirmation-hearing-donald-trumps-fbi-chief-pick-pledges-reform-vows-transparency%2Famp_articleshow%2F117748384.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fkash-patel-confirmation-hearing-donald-trumps-fbi-chief-pick-pledges-reform-vows-transparency%2Famp_articleshow%2F117748384.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rohit%20Won't%20Have%20To%20Set%20Foot%20On%20Pak%20Soil%20For%20CT%202025%20As%20ICC%2C%20PCB%20Cancel...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhether%20or%20not%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20go%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20captains'%20meet%20has%20been%20a%20matter%20of%20intense%20speculation.%20The%20BCCI%20was%20against%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20going%20to%20Pakistan%20-%20the%20designated%20hosts%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20-%20and%20hence%20the%20tournament%20was%20shifted%20to%20a%20hybrid%20model%2C%20where%20India's%20games%20will%20be%20played%20in%20Dubai.%20Then%20came%20the%20issue%20of%20Rohit%20Sharma%20travelling%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20customary%20captains'%20meet%20-%20a%20common%20practice%20ahead%20of%20any%20big%20ICC%20event.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cricbuzz.com%2Fcricket-news%2F133269%2Fno-opening-ceremony-for-ct-2025-rohit-need-not-go-to-pakistan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECricbuzz%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20claimed%20that%20Rohit%20Sharma%20will%20not%20have%20to%20go%20to%20Champions%20Trophy%20as%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20and%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20have%20cancelled%20the%20planned%20opening%20ceremony%20or%20captains%20photo-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20it%20quoted%20a%20source%20as%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BAn%20opening%20ceremony%20was%20never%20announced%20either%20by%20the%20ICC%20or%20the%20PCB.%20The%20last%20opening%20ceremony%20with%20all%20the%20participating%20players%20taking%20part%20was%20held%20in%20Dhaka%202011.%20Never%20after.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20report%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI%20quoted%20a%20source%20as%20saying%20the%20PCB%20was%20forced%20to%20cancel%20the%20pre-tournament%20captains'%20gathering%20because%20of%20%26quot%3Bunavailability%20of%20teams%20due%20to%20tight%20travelling%20schedules.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20thing%20is%20all%20teams%20have%20tight%20schedules%20before%20the%20tournament.%20England%20and%20India%20are%20playing%20a%20white-ball%20series%20while%20Australia%20is%20playing%20a%20Test%20and%20ODI%20series%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20the%20PCB%20will%20organise%20an%20inauguration%20event%20for%20the%20tournament%20on%20February%2016%20in%20Lahore%20instead%20of%20an%20official%20opening%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20tradition%2C%20captains%20of%20all%20participating%20teams%20gather%20for%20a%20pre-tournament%20photo-op%20before%20the%20start%20of%20an%20ICC%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202025%20edition%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20which%20is%20set%20to%20be%20played%20from%20February%2019%20to%20March%209%2C%20will%20be%20held%20across%20three%20venues%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20one%20in%20Dubai.%