layers%2F1109-ravichandran-ashwin-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavichandran%20Ashwin%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20not%20only%20a%20spin%20great.%20But%20he%20is%20a%20thinker.%20A%20strategist.%20A%20motivator.%20In%20his%20early%20days.%20The%20young%20Ashwin%20was%20one%20bowlers%20who%20never%20shied%20away%20from%20trying%20out%20variations%20in%20his%20bowling.%20so%20much%20so%20that%20even%20the%20great%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20to%20ask%20him%20to%20reply%20more%20on%20his%20stock%20delivery.%20Ashwin%20went%20on%20to%20become%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20spinners%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Indian%20cricket.%20The%20amount%20of%20research%20that%20he%20did%20in%20decoding%20a%20batter's%20technique%20is%20insane.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20this%20one%20time%20when%20Ashwin%20was%20trying%20to%20understand%20the%20nuances%20of%20Steve%20Smtih's%20batting%20technique%2C%20he%20got%20so%20involved%2C%20that%20his%20wife%20Prithi%20was%20concerned.%20The%20former%20India%20star%2C%20who%20retired%20recently%2C%20said%20that%20Prithi%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20faulted%20for%20thinking%20he%20had%20a%20'man%20crush'%20on%20Steve%20Smith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20him%20out%20him%20in%20Australia.%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20many%20times%20I%20watched%20Steve%20Smith%20bat%2C%20I%20can't%20even%20remember.%20My%20wife%20was%20in%20the%20room%2C%20my%20kids%20were%20in%20the%20room.%20I%20don't%20think%20I%20saw%20them%20properly%20at%20all%20for%20a%20few%20days.%20Like%20I%20kept%20zooming%20in%20on%20something%2C%20my%20wife%20watched%20from%20behind%20and%20said%20'what%20the%20hell%20are%20you%20watching%3F%20Why%20you%20going%20so%20close%20on%20Steve%20Smith%3F%20Do%20you%20have%20like%20a...'.%20I%20think%20she%20was%20concerned%20and%20rightly%20so.%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20faulted%20her%20if%20she%20thought%20I%20had%20a%20man%20crush%20on%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fawsaiconclaveonline.virtual.awsevents.com%2Fmedia%2FAWS%2520AI%2520Conclave%25202025%2520Bengaluru%2520keynote%2520recap%2F1_ksy1wsk4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAWS%20AI%20Conclave%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20so%20close.%20I%20was%20actually%20zooming%20in%20on%20his%20hands.%20I%20genuinely%20needed%20more%20people%20or%20more%20data%20or%20more%20intervention%20to%20help%20me%20out%20with%20that%20but%20I%20didn't%20have%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20all-rounder%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20recently%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20England's%20poor%20batting%20performance%20in%20the%20T20I%20series%20and%20even%20compared%20it%20to%20driving%20in%20Bengaluru's%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20stated%20that%20the%202022%20T20%20World%20Cup%20champions%20need%20to%20understand%20the%20pitch%20conditions%20rather%20than%20always%20playing%20their%20attacking%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEngland%20has%20played%20incomplete%20cricket.%20They%20made%20a%20series%20of%20mistakes.%20When%20you%20play%20in%20India%2C%20you%20can't%20play%20in%20one%20tempo.%20If%20you%20drive%20in%20Bengaluru%20traffic%2C%20you%20can't%20always%20be%20in%20the%20fourth%20gear.%20It's%20the%20same%20logic%20here.%20Sometimes%2C%20you%20can't%20even%20go%20to%20the%20fourth%20gear%20in%20Bengaluru%20(laughs)%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738249500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F9ct7ubb_ashwin-and-prithi-bcci_625x300_23_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwhat-are-you-watching-ravichandran-ashwin-on-wife-prithis-man-crush-concern-7597009%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20amount%20of%20research%20that%20Ravichandran%