Hawk%20helicopter%2C%20asking%20if%20it%20could%20see%20the%20airplane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPat%202-5%2C%20pass%20behind%20the%20CRJ%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20controller%20requested.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGasps%20could%20then%20be%20heard%20moments%20later%2C%20with%20one%20voice%20asking%20%26quot%3Btower%2C%20did%20you%20see%20that%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20saw%20a%20fireball%20and%20then%20it%20was%20just%20gone.%20I%20haven't%20seen%20anything%20since%20they%20hit%20the%20river.%20But%20it%20was%20a%20CRJ%20and%20a%20helicopter%20that%20hit%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20air%20traffic%20controller%20said%20after%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airplane%20would%20have%20had%20the%20right%20of%20way%20if%20it%20was%20cleared%20to%20land%2C%20Kyle%20Bailey%2C%20a%20pilot%20and%20aviation%20expert%2C%20told%20Fox%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20other%20officials%20stressed%20they%20were%20waiting%20for%20investigations%20to%20unfold%20--%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20posted%20a%20critical%20take%20on%20the%20incident%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20airplane%20was%20on%20a%20perfect%20and%20routine%20line%20of%20approach%20to%20the%20airport.%20The%20helicopter%20was%20going%20straight%20at%20the%20airplane%20for%20an%20extended%20period%20of%20time.%20It%20is%20a%20CLEAR%20NIGHT%2C%20the%20lights%20on%20the%20plane%20were%20blazing%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Trump%20wrote%20on%20his%20Truth%20Social%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20didn't%20the%20helicopter%20go%20up%20or%20down%2C%20or%20turn.%20Why%20didn't%20the%20control%20tower%20tell%20the%20helicopter%20what%20to%20do%20instead%20of%20asking%20if%20they%20saw%20the%20plane.%20This%20is%20a%20bad%20situation%20that%20looks%20like%20it%20should%20have%20been%20prevented.%20NOT%20GOOD!!!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmerican%20Airlines'%20chief%20executive%20Robert%20Isom%20expressed%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20sorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20w