B%20Co%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20irony%20wasn't%20lost%20on%20many.%20Musk%2C%20who%20just%20days%20earlier%20had%20courted%20controversy%20for%20a%20gesture%20at%20Donald%20Trump's%20inauguration%20likened%20by%20some%20to%20a%20Nazi%20salute%2C%20now%20stood%20as%20the%20keynote%20virtual%20guest%20for%20a%20party%20deemed%20a%20%E2%80%9Cright-wing%20extremist%E2%80%9D%20organisation%20by%20German%20security%20services.%20Adding%20fuel%20to%20the%20fire%2C%20Musk%20openly%20endorsed%20the%20AfD%2C%20declaring%3A%20%E2%80%9CI'm%20very%20excited%20for%20the%20AfD%3B%20I%20think%20you're%20really%20the%20best%20hope%20for%20Germany.%20Fight%20for%20a%20great%20future%20for%20Germany.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20endorsement%20marked%20Musk's%20second%20high-profile%20engagement%20with%20the%20far-Right%20party%20in%20recent%20weeks.%20Just%20days%20before%20that%2C%20he%20had%20interviewed%20party%20leader%20Alice%20Weidel%20on%20X%2C%20stoking%20concerns%20over%20election%20interference%20and%20platform%20bias.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Teetering%20World%20Order%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20minds%20of%20the%20European%20establishment%2C%20Musk's%20defiant%20foray%20into%20German%20politics%20raises%20a%20larger%2C%20more%20ominous%20question%3A%20is%20this%20a%20preview%20of%20a%20new%20wave%20of%20transatlantic%20populism%2C%20with%20tech%20'oligarchs'%20cheerleading%20their%20master%20in%20the%20White%20House%3F%20Ditching%20guilt%20might%20sit%20well%20with%20certain%20segments%20of%20Germany%20and%20Europe%2C%20but%20it%20strikes%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20European%20project.%20The%20European%20Union%2C%20for%20all%20its%20flaws%2C%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20built%20on%20a%20foundation%20of%20historical%20reckoning%E2%80%94a%20conscious%20effort%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20horrors%20of%20the%2020th%20century%20are%20neither%20forgotten%20nor%20repeated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20President%20Trump's%20return%20to%20power%2C%20Europe%20finds%20itself%20confronting%20an%20emboldened%20America%2C%20where%20the%20transatlantic%20relationship%20seems%20less%20about%20partnership%20and%20shared%20values%20and%20more%20about%20power%20plays%20and%20transactional%20diplomacy.%20For%20many%20across%20the%20continent%2C%20it%20feels%20as%20if%20the%20whims%20of%20billionaires%20and%20a%20president%20unbound%20by%20the%20traditional%20Western%20playbook%20now%20dictate%20the%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post-World%20War%20II%20order%2C%20once%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20global%20stability%2C%20is%20teetering%20on%20the%20brink.%20Trump's%20statements%20on%20NATO%20and%20Europe%2C%20and%20his%20sweeping%20actions%20in%20just%20the%20first%20week%20of%20his%20new%20term%2C%20have%20sent%20shockwaves%20through%20European%20capitals.%20It's%20clear%20that%20Trump%20has%20returned%20with%20a%20sharper%20focus%20and%20a%20steely%20resolve%20to%20assert%20American%20dominance.%20A%20striking%20example%20came%20on%20Sunday%20when%20news%20broke%20that%20Trump%20had%20imposed%20a%20staggering%2025%25%20tariff%20on%20Colombia%2C%20one%20of%20America's%20closest%20allies%20and%20its%20largest%20trading%20partner%20in%20Latin%20America.%20The%20reason%20was%20the%20country's%20refusal%20to%20allow%20US%20military%20planes%20carrying%20undocumented%20Colombian%20immigrants%20to%20land%20on%20its%20soil.%20The%20move%2C%20viewed%20with%20dismay%20in%20Europe%2C%20looked%20like%20a%20stark%20warning%20to%20both%20friends%20and%20foes%3A%20cooperate%20or%20face%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump%20Means%20Business%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20European%20leaders%2C%20the%20message%20is%20unmissable.%20Trump's%20second%20term%20is%20about%20forcing%20others%20to%20toe%20America's%20line%20through%20sheer%20economic%20and%20political%20leverage.%20This%20bold%E2%80%94and%20many%20would%20say%20reckless%E2%80%94approach%20leaves%20Europe%20grappling%20with%20the%20unsettling%20reality%20that%20even%20long-standing%20allies%20aren't%20immune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEU%20leaders%20and%20policymakers%20are%20scrambling%20to%20recalibrate%20their%20approach%20to%20a%20transatlantic%20relationship%20that%20appears%20increasingly%20one-sided.%20Trump's%20demands%E2%80%94slashing%20tariffs%20on%20American%20goods%2C%20forcing%20countries%20to%20raise%20their%20NATO%20contributions%2C%20and%20rolling%20back%20regulations%20on%20American%20tech%20giants%E2%80%94are%20reshaping%20US-EU%20dynamics.%20Unlike%20Joe%20Biden's%20coalition-driven%20diplomacy%2C%20Trump's%20second%20term%20threatens%20to%20redefine%20the%20relationship%20as%20one%20of%20coercion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEurope%2C%20however%2C%20has%20only%20itself%20to%20blame.%20While%20China%20quietly%20fortified%20itself%20for%20Trump's%20potential%20return%2C%20Europe%20failed%20to%20draw%20lessons%20from%20his%20first%20term.%20Despite%20enduring%20his%20bullish%20style%2C%20the%20continent%20made%20little%20effort%20to%20prepare%20for%20his%20resurgence.%20Now%2C%20European%20leaders%20are%20left%20grappling%20with%20a%20key%20question%3A%20how%20much%20of%20Trump's%20rhetoric%20is%20posturing%2C%20and%20how%20much%20is%20a%20prelude%20to%20action%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20few%20European%20leaders%20to%20recognise%20the%20growing%20vulnerability%20of%20the%20continent%20is%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron.%20He%20has%20long%20warned%20of%20the%20need%20for%20a%20stronger%2C%20more%20self-reliant%20Europe.%20Last%20year%2C%20he%20famously%20declared%2C%20%E2%80%9CEurope%20can%20die%2C%20and%20that%20depends%20entirely%20on%20our%20choices.%E2%80%9D%20Yet%2C%20despite%20Macron's%20calls%20for%20resilience%2C%20Europe%20remains%20deeply%20fractured%20and%2C%20many%20believe%2C%20is%20in%20a%20weaker%20position%20to%20face%20Trump%202.0%20than%20it%20was%20during%20his%20first%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Transatlantic%20Tightrope%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETariffs%20and%20Trade%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETrump%20has%20long%20criticised%20what%20he%20sees%20as%20Europe's%20protectionist%20policies%2C%20particularly%20its%20tariffs%20on%20American%20goods.%20At%20Davos%20last%20week%2C%20he%20zeroed%20in%20on%20European%20duties%20on%20American%20cars%2C%20calling%20them%20unfair%20and%20warning%20of%20punitive%20actions%20if%20his%20demands%20for%20lower%20tariffs%20are%20not%20met.%20This%20aggressive%20posturing%20could%20spark%20trade%20tensions%20reminiscent%20of%20his%20first%20term%2C%20when%20tariff%20wars%20strained%20global%20markets.%20But%20the%20US%20President%20has%20a%20point.%20The%20European%20Union%20imposes%20a%2010%25%20tariff%20on%20imported%20American%20cars%2C%20while%20the%20US%20applies%20a%20lower%20tariff%20of%202.5%25%20on%20cars%20imported%20from%20the%20EU.%20This%20disparity%20has%20been%20a%20significant%20point%20of%20contention%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENATO%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDuring%20his%20first%20presidency%2C%20Trump%20accused%20NATO%20members%20of%20freeloading%20off%20the%20US%20defence%20budget.%20Now%2C%20he%20is%20back%20with%20even%20more%20audacious%20demands.%20Trump%20has%20called%20for%20NATO%20members%20to%20contribute%205%25%20of%20their%20GDP%20to%20defence%E2%80%94a%20figure%20so%20high%20it%20would%20strain%20the%20budgets%20of%20even%20the%20wealthiest%20nations%20of%20Europe.%20Trump's%20transactional%20approach%20to%20defence%20funding%20reduces%20the%20alliance%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpay-to-play%E2%80%9D%20arrangement%2C%20fundamentally%20altering%20its%20spirit%20of%20collective%20security.%20The%20implicit%20threat%20is%20stark%2C%20comply%20or%20face%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20US%20questioning%20NATO's%20very%20relevance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETech%20Regulation%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETrump's%20disdain%20for%20Europe's%20stringent%20regulations%20on%20US%20tech%20giants%20is%20no%20secret.%20At%20Davos%2C%20he%20singled%20out%20Google%2C%20accusing%20Europe%20of%20stifling%20American%20innovation%20with%20excessive%20fines%20and%20red%20tape.%20By%20framing%20this%20as%20an%20attack%20on%20American%20enterprise%2C%20Trump%20challenges%20Europe's%20sovereign%20right%20to%20govern%20its%20digital%20markets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20Europe%20Bowing%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20European%20leaders%20have%20treaded%20lightly%2C%20avoiding%20direct%20confrontation%20with%20Trump.%20Publicly%2C%20they%20emphasise%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20transatlantic%20bond%20with%20warm%20words%2C%20even%20as%20his%20demands%20grow%20more%20unreasonable.%20But%20behind%20the%20diplomatic%20smiles%20lies%20a%20palpable%20unease.%20European%20leaders%20and%20experts%20fear%20that%20continued%20acquiescence%20will%20erode%20their%20foundational%20principles%20of%20sovereignty%2C%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20the%20collective%20strength%20derived%20from%20unity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20press%2C%20often%20vocal%20on%20transatlantic%20matters%2C%20has%20also%20been%20unusually%20subdued%2C%20reflecting%20a%20broader%20reluctance%20to%20provoke%20Trump.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20silence%2C%20as%20history%20teaches%20us%2C%20comes%20with%20a%20cost.%20Europe%20faces%20a%20moment%20of%20reckoning.%20Should%20it%20play%20second%20fiddle%20to%20an%20increasingly%20assertive%20US%3F%20Or%20should%20it%20push%20back%2C%20risking%20the%20relationship%20but%20asserting%20its%20sovereignty%20and%20values%3F%20The%20ancient%20Greek%20historian%20and%20war%20chronicler%2C%20Thucydides%2C%20would've%20perhaps%20described%20it%20thus%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20strong%20do%20what%20they%20can%2C%20and%20the%20weak%20suffer%20what%20they%20must.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(%3Cem%3ESyed%20Zubair%20Ahmed%20is%20a%20London-based%20senior%20Indian%20journalist%20with%20three%20decades%20of%20experience%20with%20the%20Western%20media)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738238160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fpro9j158_trump_625x300_30_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-one-where-europe-gets-bullied-7595672%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Europe%20faces%20a%20moment%20of%20reckoning.%20Should%20it%20play%20second%20fiddle%20to%20an%20increasingly%20assertive%20US%20under%20Trump%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-one-where-europe-gets-bullied-7595672%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Deportation%20Flight%20For%20Each%20Migrant%20Likely%20Costs%20More%20Than%20First%20Class%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20military%20deportation%20flight%20to%20Guatemala%20on%20Monday%20likely%20cost%20at%20least%20%244%2C675%20per%20migrant%2C%20according%20to%20data%20provided%20by%20US%20and%20Guatemalan%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20more%20than%20five%20times%20the%20%24853%20cost%20of%20a%20one-way%20first%20class%20ticket%20on%20American%20Airlines%20from%20El%20Paso%2C%20Texas%2C%20the%20departure%20point%20for%20the%20flight%2C%20according%20to%20a%20review%20of%20publicly%20available%20airfares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20significantly%20higher%20than%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20commercial%20charter%20flight%20by%20US%20Immigration%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%20(ICE).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20launched%20the%20military%20deportation%20flights%20last%20week%20as%20part%20of%20his%20national%20emergency%20declaration%20on%20immigration%2C%20so%20far%20sending%20six%20planeloads%20of%20migrants%20on%20flights%20to%20Latin%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20four%20have