0sending%20a%20strong%20and%20clear%20message%20to%20the%20entire%20world%3A%20if%20you%20illegally%20enter%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America%2C%20you%20will%20face%20severe%20consequences.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHIGH%20PRICE%20TAG%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20C-17%20price%20tag%20is%20substantially%20higher%20than%20the%20alternative%3A%20commercial%20aircraft%20chartered%20by%20ICE.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECosts%20for%20the%20charter%20ICE%20flights%20vary.%20According%20to%20information%20posted%20on%20ICE's%20website%20in%202021%2C%20the%20cost%20for%20%26quot%3BIce%20Air%26quot%3B%20flights%20is%20%248%2C577%20per%20flight%20hour.%20But%20acting%20ICE%20Director%20Tae%20Johnson%20told%20lawmakers%20during%20an%20April%202023%20budget%20hearing%20that%20deportation%20flights%20cost%20%2417%2C000%20per%20flight%20hour%20for%20135%20deportees%20and%20typically%20lasted%20five%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20higher%20figure%20given%20by%20Johnson%20would%20translate%20to%20a%20cost%20of%20%24630%20per%20person%2C%20assuming%20the%20charter%20company%2C%20and%20not%20ICE%2C%20pays%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20return%20flight.%20A%20former%20ICE%20official%20said%20the%20cost%20had%20risen%20slightly%20since%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EICE%20says%20it%20transports%20detainees%20on%20chartered%20Boeing%20737%20or%20McDonnell%20Douglas%20MD-80%20series%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pentagon%20said%20last%20week%20the%20US%20military%20would%20provide%20flights%20for%20the%20deportations%20of%20more%20than%205%2C000%20immigrants%20held%20by%20US%20authorities%20in%20El%20Paso%2C%20Texas%2C%20and%20San%20Diego%2C%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738238160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2