t%20Rs%2036%2C020%20under%20the%207th%20Pay%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20suggest%20that%20the%20fitment%20factor%20could%20rise%20to%202.86%2C%20which%20will%20raise%20the%20basic%20pay%20in%20Level%201%20from%20Rs%2018%2C000%20to%20Rs%2051%2C480.%20Accordingly%2C%20at%20all%2010%20levels%2C%20employees%20will%20see%20a%20revision%20in%20salaries%20and%20pensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESalary%20Hike%20You%20Can%20Expect%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20%3Cstrong%3ELevel%201%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20which%20includes%20peons%2C%20attendants%2C%20and%20support%20staff%2C%20the%20basic%20pay%20of%20Rs%2018%2C000%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20revised%20to%20Rs%2051%2C480%2C%20an%20increase%20of%20Rs%2033%2C480.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20%3Cstrong%3ELevel%202%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Rs%2019%2C900%20basic%20pay%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20raised%20to%20Rs%2056%2C914%2C%20a%20raise%20of%20Rs%2037%2C014.%20Lower%20division%20clerks%20who%20manage%20clerical%20duties%20fall%20at%20this%20level.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20%3Cstrong%3ELevel%203%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20the%20basic%20pay%20of%20Rs%2021%2C700%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20raised%20to%20Rs%2062%2C062%2C%20an%20increase%20of%20Rs%2040%2C362.%20Constables%20and%20skilled%20staff%20in%20the%20police%20or%20public%20services%20are%20included%20under%20this%20level.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20%3Cstrong%3ELevel%204%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20which%20includes%20Grade%20D%20stenographers%20and%20junior%20clerks%2C%20Rs%2025%2C500%20basic%20pay%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20increased%20to%20Rs%2072%2C930%2C%20an%20increase%20of%20Rs%2047%2C430.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20%3Cstrong%3ELevel%205%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20the%20basic%20pay%20of%20Rs%2029%2C200%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20revised%20to%20Rs%2083%2C512%2C%20an%20increase%20of%20Rs%2054%2C312.%20Senior%20clerks%20and%20higher-level%20technical%20staff%20are%20included%20in%20this%20category.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20%3Cstrong%3ELevel%206%3C%2Fstrong%3E%